## Howto build

1. check the [dependencies](https://gluon.readthedocs.org/en/latest/user/getting_started.html#dependencies) and install missing
2. follow this script

```bash
# bisher nehmen wir den Branch master:
git clone https://github.com/freifunk-gluon/gluon.git
cd gluon
git clone https://github.com/c3d2/gluon-site.git
mv gluon-site site
echo "PACKAGES_DDMESH_REPO=git://github.com/c3d2/gluon-packages.git" >> modules
# Bauen:
make update
make GLUON_TARGET=x86-generic
```

[Mehr Doku](http://gluon.readthedocs.org/en/latest/user/getting_started.html#building-the-images)
